Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.radio

Interface RadioService

All Superinterfaces:
Insertion
All Known Implementing Classes:
RadioServiceImpl
public interface RadioService extends Insertion
Provides an interface for interacting with radio button elements in a UI automation framework, enabling operations like selection, state verification, and retrieving lists of available radios. By referencing a RadioComponentType and the DEFAULT_TYPE, implementations can uniformly identify and control radio buttons in various application contexts.

Classes implementing this interface typically leverage Selenium-based approaches for container/locator handling, ensuring consistent behavior across different UI designs.
